<%- include('../partials/html-head') %>
<%- include('../partials/nav') %>

<main>
  <h1>Welcome to the Cocktail Rolodex</h1>
  <h2> <%=  user.profile.name %></h2>
<div class="show-text">
  <p>The Cocktail Rolodex was developed with two main ideas in mind : </p>
  <ol>
    <li> Furthering my education in building full stack applications building while also utilizing an external API and data</li>
    <li> To explore some new cocktails or ideas to try later</li>
  </ol>  
  <h2>Future Features:</h2>
  <ul>
  <li>Light and dark mode</li>
  <li>Mobile app display improvements</li>
  <li>Allow users to add ratings to cocktails</li>
  <li>Sort cocktails by frequency and weight of ratings</li>
  <li>Search by base liquor</li>
  <li>View a list of cocktails comparing all ratings of all users saved cocktails to show top 10</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div id="random-cocktail" class="landing-page">
<section id="Random-cocktail">
<h3>Feeling adventurous maybe you would like a random beverage</h3>
<form action="/cocktails/random" method="POST">
  <button class="btn btn-warning btn-lg btn-block">Random Cocktail</button>
</form>
</div>

<div  id="seach-cocktail" class="landing-page" >
  <h3>If not, let's find you your drinks of choice</h3>
  
  <form action="/cocktails/search" method="get">
    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Search Cocktails</button>
  </form>
</div>

  <div id="redirect-to-rolodex" class="landing-page">
    <h3>Or Head to your Saved cocktails!</h3>
    <form action="/profiles" method="get">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg btn-block">View Rolodex</button>
    </form>
  </div>

</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>